      "SummaryText": "was taken into account in evaluating these scenarios.\n\n\nFive- Year Accident History\n\nThe Oiltanking Marine Terminal, in the past five (5) years, has not incurred any chemical releases that resulted in any known onsite or offsite deaths, injuries, significant damage, evacuations or sheltering in place, property damage or environmental damage.   \n\n\nAccidental Release Prevention Policies\n\nThe plans for evacuation and accounting for personnel after an evacuation at Oiltanking Marine Terminal, are located onsite for all personnel to review.\n\nIf a release occurs,  arrangements in described in the Emergency Response Plan for notif                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       